message:
{{#is_alert}}
🔴 [P1 CRITICAL] More than 3 applications are in Degraded state

Degraded count: {{value}}
Multiple applications are unhealthy simultaneously. This likely indicates a systemic issue — cluster connectivity, shared dependency failure, or controller problem.

Actions:
1. Check cluster connectivity on Application Operations dashboard
2. Check ArgoCD controller health on Host Cluster dashboard
3. Identify affected apps and common patterns (same cluster? same addon type?)
4. Review controller logs for widespread errors
